[SHORT DESC]
Summons sun for 5 turns.

[LONG DESC]
<p>Summons sunlight for 5 turns. While in effect, it increases the damage of Fire-type 
moves by 50%, and causes Water moves to do half damage. Thunder is 50% accurate. 
Solarbeam has no charge turn. Moonlight, Morning Sun, and Synthesis heal 2/3 of 
the user's maximum HP. No Pokémon can be Frozen while the Sunlight is active. Pokémon with the Chlorophyll ability have double Speed. Pokémon with the Forecast ability become Fire-type.</p>
<h2>Related Moves</h2>
<p><a href="/rs/moves/hail">Hail</a> is an Ice-type equivalent.<br/ >
<a href="/rs/moves/rain_dance">Rain Dance</a> is a Water-type equivalent.<br/ >
<a href="/rs/moves/sandstorm">Sandstorm</a> is a Rock-type equivalent.</p>